reviewText: Great show, the box set is simple and very nice. Lots of extras, deleted scenes and behind the scenes too!
This two box DVD set is awesome. It has a lot of the episodes that I love. It includes Bad Moon Rising and Boob Job. Those episodea are hilarious! Good deal for all what you get.

Starting watching season 4 last night. The first show played normal. The next shows, on the entire disk, skipped. We were moving forward to a different scene so many times only to have that scene skip, and that was only disk 1.  Considering very strongly in returning item. Need to try Season 5 first.

My mom loves this show, it is her favorite, so I have been buying them season by season. This is a good deal, the 2 in one package thing. Giving it to her for Christmas. I am sure she will love it as usual.
